            <p class="text-light-bg-alt dark:text-dark-bg-alt">
              AI models form their understanding from publicly available information. Ensure accurate representation.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
            <div class="text-5xl mb-4">ðŸš€</div>
