            <p class="text-light-bg-alt dark:text-dark-bg-alt">
              While 80% of businesses ignore AI optimization, early adopters are capturing market share.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
            <div class="text-5xl mb-4">ðŸ’¡</div>
